# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# AgroManager Pro — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values
# NEVER commit .env to version control
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── Supabase (REQUIRED) ──────────────────────────────────────
# Found in: Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → API

# Your Supabase project URL
# Format: https://[your-project-ref].supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://xjlleutsqkxibvkdfaij.supabase.co

# Your Supabase anon/public key (safe to use on frontend)
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# ─── App Config (OPTIONAL) ────────────────────────────────────
VITE_APP_NAME=AgroManager Pro
VITE_APP_URL=http://localhost:5173

# ─── Feature Flags (OPTIONAL) ─────────────────────────────────
VITE_ENABLE_REALTIME=true
VITE_ENABLE_ANALYTICS=true

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# 1. Create a free Supabase project at https://supabase.com
#    (No credit card required for free tier)
#
# 2. In your Supabase project:
#    a. Go to SQL Editor and run supabase/schema.sql
#    b. Go to SQL Editor and run supabase/seed.sql
#    c. In Authentication > Settings, disable email confirmation
#       for easier local development
#
# 3. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env
#    Fill in VITE_SUPABASE_URL and VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
#
# 4. Install dependencies: npm install
#
# 5. Start dev server: npm run dev
#
# 6. Demo login credentials:
#    Admin: admin@agromanager.demo / Admin@2025
#    Staff: staff@agromanager.demo / Staff@2025
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# VERCEL DEPLOYMENT
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# In Vercel Dashboard → Project Settings → Environment Variables,
# add the same variables WITHOUT the VITE_ prefix workaround.
# Vercel DOES support VITE_ prefixed vars for Vite projects.
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
